text: The Conachi family was a Moldavian boyar family, with Phanariote origin,Gălăţeni care au uimit lumea or, according to others, of Moldavian high nobility (răzeș) origin. ==Notable members== *Costache Conachi, writer, poet, engineer, and politician (Great Logothete of Moldavia) *Ecaterina Cocuța Conachi, activist and revolutionary ==References== ==External links== Category:Phanariotes Category:Romanian boyar families Category:Moldavian nobility
title: Conachi family
